Photos Screen
- I would like to expand this to create a responsive design for tablets, and foldables. We would accomplish
    this through the use of WindowSizeClass which will be particularly important from Android 17+
    - The most significant change in design would be to use a grid for larger screen size, reducing the
        users need to scroll.

- I would also look to move the search filtering over to the 'Ready' state holder (with more appropriate naming)
    - I wanted to leave the current implementation as it showcases combining flows that would be responsive
        to both the search, and product/photo data changing. Although in this case, the data never changes.